!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
#tmass      172.5d0                              ! (default 172.5) top quark mass (in the matrix ele
#tmass_phsp 172.5d0                              ! (default 172.5) top quark mass (in the phase spac
#twidth                                          ! (default unset) top quark width (calculated from
